Package: AtmoTubeR
Type: Package
Title: Tools to access and manipulate sensor data from portable AtmoTube personal air monitors
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Neil Klepeis
Maintainer: Neil Klepeis <software@klepeis.net>
Description: This package has functions to read and plot sensor streams and locations
    for portable AtmoTube air monitoring devices (e.g., the AtmoTube Pro) 
    based on established formats and published API's.  Sensor data include particulates, VOC's, 
    temperature, pressure, and humidity - as well as GPS coordinates.
Imports: tidyr,dplyr,jsonlite,ggplot2,lubridate,maps,sp,osmdata,sf,timetk,googlesheets4,leaflet,sensoRplot,readr
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.2)
